34
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:47,640
I'll get it.

35
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:48,700
Perfect.

36
00:01:49,180 --> 00:01:50,640
As long as you get that seal,

37
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,620
I'll give you

38
