whatever you want.

39
00:01:52,659 --> 00:01:53,159
Really?

40
00:02:04,900 --> 00:02:07,140
Want me to approve East Suburb project?

41
00:02:07,140 --> 00:02:08,520
Forget about it!

42
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:10,580
Kuntai,

43
