94
00:03:56,219 --> 00:03:58,280
You've researched me well.

95
00:03:58,460 --> 00:03:59,080
What?

96
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:00,960
Coming after me now?

97
00:04:03,659 --> 00:04:05,460
You have this condition,

98
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,240
because 30 years ago,

99
00:04:07,580 --> 00:04:08,860
you saved me from the icy river.

100
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:10,719
Back then,

101
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,000
your right leg

102
00:04:13,379 --> 00:04:15,419
were suffering from severe rheumatism.

103
00:04:16,060 --> 00:04:17,459
