105
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:23,980
I never told anyone about this,

106
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:26,699
not even the former chairman.

107
00:04:27,879 --> 00:04:29,319
How did you find out?

108
00:04:30,879 --> 00:04:31,500
Mr. Kuntai,

109
00:04:31,939 --> 00:04:33,040
I really am Lin Xia!

110
00:04:33,319 --> 00:04:34,220
Impossible!

111
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:37,139
You must've captured and tortured her.

112
00:04:37,699 --> 00:04:38,879
You all deserve to die!

113
00:04:42,959 --> 00:04:44,319
I used Bai Cha's appearance.

114
00:04:45,819 --> 00:04:46,920
With this new identity,

115
00:04:47,319 --> 00:04:48,860
I'll take revenge on Ye Dong.

116
00:04:56,819 --> 00:04:57,319
Look at

117
00:04:59,019 --> 00:05:00,180
the video of the procedure.

118
00:05:14,660 --> 00:05:15,459
You...

119
00:05:15,459 --> 00:05:16,360
You're Lin Xia.

120
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:19,699
You're really Xia.

121
00:05:20,420 --> 00:05:20,920
Yes,

122
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,560
I'm Xia.

123
00:05:24,899 --> 00:05:25,920
As long as you're safe.

124
00:05:26,779 --> 00:05:27,980
Being alive is enough.

125
00:05:28,379 --> 00:05:28,879
So great!

126
00:05:30,560 --> 00:05:31,899
With your testimony,

127
00:05:32,420 --> 00:05:34,560
I'll put Ye Dong behind bars.

128
00:05:39,459 --> 00:05:40,379
Right now

129
00:05:42,519 --> 00:05:44,120
we can't do that.

130
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:45,680
Why?

131
00:05:50,980 --> 00:05:53,120
He and his mother killed my father

132
00:05:53,819 --> 00:05:55,019
and Lin Na

133
00:05:55,300 --> 00:05:56,500
and caused Bai Cha's death.

134
00:05:57,819 --> 00:05:59,420
Putting him in jail now

135
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:01,220
is letting him off lightly.

136
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:03,160
Xia,

137
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,560
what's your plan?

138
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:08,560
We need

139
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:12,459
to unite with other shareholders

140
00:06:13,139 --> 00:06:14,319
to gain absolute

141
00:06:15,319 --> 00:06:16,680
decision-making power.

142
00:06:23,060 --> 00:06:24,420
Alright.

143
00:06:31,959 --> 00:06:32,600
Mom,

144
00:06:32,899 --> 00:06:34,259
you've recovered enough.

145
00:06:34,420 --> 00:06:35,360
Let's go home.

146
00:06:35,740 --> 00:06:36,379
The company

147
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,300
has many matters waiting for me.

148
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:42,060
You haven't spent a full month with me.

149
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,500
You're not going anywhere.

150
00:06:43,660 --> 00:06:44,240
Otherwise,

151
00:06:44,420 --> 00:06:45,839
I'll disown you as my son.

152
00:06:50,540 --> 00:06:51,160
Fine.

153
00:06:51,899 --> 00:06:52,699
I'll obey.

154
00:06:54,860 --> 00:06:56,019
After I'm discharged,

155
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:58,519
I'll arrange your wedding with Wei.

156
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,920
Cut ties with

157
00:07:02,100 --> 00:07:03,079
those random women.

158
00:07:06,319 --> 00:07:07,079
Let's

159
00:07:07,379 --> 00:07:08,259
discuss it later.

160
00:07:09,579 --> 00:07:10,560
This matter

161
00:07:10,699 --> 00:07:12,420
is non-negotiable.

162
00:07:12,759 --> 00:07:13,800
Wei's destiny

163
00:07:14,259 --> 00:07:15,759
aligns perfectly with yours.

164
00:07:16,540 --> 00:07:18,000
If you two marry,

165
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:19,579
our Ye family

166
00:07:19,819 --> 00:07:21,819
will reach new heights.

167
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:26,500
Are you still thinking about that woman?

168
00:07:27,699 --> 00:07:28,740
I'm warning you

169
00:07:28,899 --> 00:07:29,899
that tramp

170
00:07:29,899 --> 00:07:31,120
is bad luck.

171
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,600
She'll bring misfortune to you

172
00:07:33,720 --> 00:07:35,139
and even me.

173
00:07:35,500 --> 00:07:36,560
Stay away from her.

174
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:37,660
Understood?

175
00:07:39,480 --> 00:07:40,240
Dong,

176
00:07:40,560 --> 00:07:41,819
help me!

177
00:07:44,259 --> 00:07:44,959
What happened?

178
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:45,660
It's

179
00:07:46,199 --> 00:07:47,019
Mu Feng.

180
00:07:47,699 --> 00:07:49,660
He used your seal to withdraw funds.

181
00:07:50,019 --> 00:07:51,420
I said I'd call you,

182
00:07:51,500 --> 00:07:52,500
but he beat me.

183
00:07:52,720 --> 00:07:54,899
He wanted the money and elope with me.

184
00:07:54,959 --> 00:07:55,660
When I refused,

185
00:07:55,660 --> 00:07:57,019
