186
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,779
Dong,

187
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,660
Mu Feng has betrayed you.

188
00:08:00,160 --> 00:08:01,259
Luckily, I was smart enough

189
00:08:01,300 --> 00:08:02,860
