192
00:08:05,759 --> 00:08:07,600
If I don't give him the money tonight,

193
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:09,259
he'll kill them.

194
00:08:09,319 --> 00:08:09,899
Dong,

195
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,959
please settle this for me!

196
00:08:13,279 --> 00:08:14,560
How dare he

197
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,959
betray me!

198
00:08:31,920 --> 00:08:33,960
Why did Yufei choose such a remote spot?

199
00:08:37,620 --> 00:08:38,419
Whatever.

200
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,159
Once I get the money,

201
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:41,419
I'll have fun with her

202
00:08:41,860 --> 00:08:43,019
and be out of here.

203
00:08:47,759 --> 00:08:48,259
Dong.

204
00:08:48,399 --> 00:08:49,080
Feng,

205
00:08:49,500 --> 00:08:51,059
